episodes.title: Simpsons Roasting on an Open Fire
episodes.plot: Homer is forced to become a department store Santa when Marge spends the family's Christmas savings on removing Bart's tattoo.

episodes.title: Bart the Genius
episodes.plot: Bart ends up at a school for gifted children after cheating on an IQ test.

episodes.title: Homer's Odyssey
episodes.plot: After losing his job, Homer contemplates ending it all, until he discovers a new life path as a safety advocate.

episodes.title: There's No Disgrace Like Home
episodes.plot: After being embarrassed by the rest of the family at a company picnic, Homer becomes obsessed with improving their behavior towards each other.

episodes.title: Bart the General
episodes.plot: After being beaten up by Nelson Muntz one too many times, Bart turns to Grampa for help, and soon leads a rebellion against the school bully.

episodes.title: Moaning Lisa
episodes.plot: A depressed Lisa's spirit is lifted when she meets a jazz-man, Bleeding Gums Murphy.

episodes.title: The Call of the Simpsons
episodes.plot: Homer takes the family camping, but it soon becomes a misadventure when they lose their equipment and Homer is mistaken for Bigfoot.

episodes.title: The Telltale Head
episodes.plot: Bart gets more than he bargained for when he saws the head off a statue of the town's founder.

episodes.title: Life on the Fast Lane
episodes.plot: Marge contemplates an affair with a handsome bowling instructor.

episodes.title: Homer's Night Out
episodes.plot: After a photograph of Homer canoodling with an exotic dancer is distributed throughout Springfield, he finds himself kicked out of the house by Marge.

episodes.title: The Crepes of Wrath
episodes.plot: Bart is sent to France on a student exchange program, where he's treated like a slave; An Albanian student takes Bart's place in the family.

episodes.title: Krusty Gets Busted
episodes.plot: After Krusty is found guilty of robbing the Kwik-E-Mart following Homer's eyewitness testimony, Bart and Lisa set out to prove his innocence.

episodes.title: Some Enchanted Evening
episodes.plot: Homer and Marge enjoy a night on the town, leaving the kids with a diabolical babysitter, with a surprising secret.
